Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To sink or swim {\fsp1}生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.97,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}dog eat dog world {\fsp1}だと言い聞かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:10.86,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:13.77,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Survival of the fittest {\fsp1}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If it's the world that our wisdom will lead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:20.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Then tell me what went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:23.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've paid my dues
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.11,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So tell me, what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.16,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}when I've given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:34.71,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:41.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:44.80,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:51.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:54.89,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:01:01.49,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:11.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.12,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}真実の見えない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}善と悪のバランスを保ち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.13,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}殺すか殺されるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:21.67,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ちっぽけな世界なのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:27.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}おい　誰か答えてみてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是沉是浮 為了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告訴他 這是同類相殘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:10.86,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:13.77,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2)}適者生存 弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果智慧能引領這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:20.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就告訴我 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:23.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已付出太多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.11,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已出賣靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:28.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告訴我 如果我放棄一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.16,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又能夠得到些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:34.71,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 這是個怎樣的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:41.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看過太多風景 卻毫無感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:44.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:51.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了追尋那個風景 我是否已毫無感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:54.89,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 這是個怎樣的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:01:01.49,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看過太多風景 卻毫無感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:11.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了追尋那個風景 我是否已毫無感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不見真相的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}維持善惡的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}殺或被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:21.67,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這世界難道這麼無趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:27.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 誰能回答我啊
